<doc id="2842782" url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=2842782" title="Straldzha">
Straldzha

Straldzha () is a small town in Yambol Province, Southeastern Bulgaria. It is the administrative centre of the homonymous Straldzha Municipality. As of December 2009, the town has a population of 6,021 inhabitants.

