<doc id="2843400" url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=2843400" title="Search EDP Inc.">
Search EDP Inc.

Search EDP Inc. is a staffing firm founded in 1983 for both full-time employees and consultants. The corporation, based in Montville, New Jersey, has the ability to source talent in all fifty U.S. states.
Although the firm started as an information technology staffing specialist, they have grown to accommodate most professions. Search EDP uses the latest in "e-cruiting" technology and has become a premier agency in the Northeastern United States.

